32500.title: A strange tunnel carved into the earth
32500.description:
You burst through the ethereal webbing into a strange tunnel like chamber.
Everything about this place forces your gaze deeper down into the depths
of the tunnel.  There are ethereal strands of webbing upon which you might
be able to find footing.  Loose clumps of dark brown clay occasionally break
loose and come tumbling down the shaft.  A sickeningly sweet smell of old
dust and rosewater is overpowering, adding to the strange sensation of
this bizarre place.
Something strange is scrawled here in slime, a sign perhaps?
You may want to take your time, as a slip in here could mean death.

32507.title: Bottom of a Strange Tunnel
32507.description:
The ethereal webbing clinging to the walls hangs loftily here, offering
a means of egress.  What appears to be a small pit has been carved out
of the earth here, and a large pool of slime collects at the base. The
stench of decay and fermentation, mixed with body odor, skunk, and other
nauseating scents is enough to turn even the most seasoned of stomachs.
There appears to be nothing else special about this chamber but your eyes
are drawn to a humming and crackling portal hovering just above the pit
of slime.  Perhaps you can make the jump through from your vantage point
on the wall.

32508.title: Vertigo
32508.description:
You step through the portal to find it seal shut behind you. When you open
your eyes, what you see borders on indescribable.  The walls and floor of
this strange place are in constant flux, spinning and oscillating wildly.
You wonder if you can even gain footing in here to make your way forward.
The walls crackle intensely with psionic energy and seem to register your
unwelcome presence with hostility.  You feel your mind exerting a constant
effort just to keep a strange presence from turning your brain to scrambled
eggs. You feel exhausted from the effort, yet the flow of mana coursing its
way through your body also seems to be increased.  The smell of rotting
things and old mildew is heavy in the air here, and every once in a while,
a strange breeze flows through this "tunnel". Or did you imagine that breeze?
In fact, you're not quite sure if you can trust yoursenses in this place with
any reliability at all. The only direction you can stumble toward is to the
east.

east.description: Your senses seem to guide you east.

32520.title: Crippling Vertigo
32520.description:
As with before, the crackling portal seals shut as you exit, leaving you in
a bewildered and disoritented state.  Your brain, barely able to focus, is
howling at you to stay alert.  Your senses all seem to be lying to you at
this point, and you feel helplessly vulnerable to attack. The walls and floor
of this strange place are in constant flux, spinning and oscillating wildly
and making your head spin. You wonder if you can even gain footing in here to
make your way forward. The walls crackle intensely with psionic energy and seem
to register your unwelcome presence with hostility. You feel your mind exerting
a constant effort just to keep a strange presence from turning your brain to
scrambled eggs. You feel exhausted from the effort, yet the flow of mana
coursing its way through your body also seems to be increased.  The smell of
rotting things and old mildew is heavy in the air here, and every once in a
while,  a strange breeze flows through this "tunnel". Or did you imagine that
breeze? In fact, you're not quite sure if you can trust yoursenses in this
place with any reliability at all. Cardinal directions have become hazy.

32531.title: At the Verge of Mental Implosion
32531.description:
It takes all of your might and a small miracle to fixate on the crackling
portal of energy in the center of this room.  Your senses are going haywire
and your brain feels like it is throbbing and hemmorhaging all at once. Your
senses have long ago stopped responding to normal stimulation, and you wonder
if maybe you should just give up and succumb to the mental pressures here, or
if you dare continue through the portal to the next layer of complete mental
anguish.

32532.title: Entrance to a Strange Chamber
32532.description:
The pressure upon your brain is fading thankfully fast into a distant
memory. As with before, the portal seals behind you, leaving you with
no choice but to proceed forward. In the distance you make out a wide
variety of strange hunched figures floating about a large open chamber
without any regard for your presence.  The walls of this place shimmer
and hum with an intense psionic energy, acting more as mental barriers
than physical ones.  The only direction in which to proceed is north.

32533.title: Within a Strange Chamber
32533.description:
In the distance you make out a wide variety of strange hunched figures
floating about a large open chamber without any regard for your presence.
The walls of this place shimmer and hum with an intense psionic energy,
acting more as mental barriers than physical ones.  It is almost as if
the architect of this place used sheer imagination and mental will to
construct the form of this area.

32534.title: Intersection the Strange Chamber
32534.description:

The walls of this place shimmer and hum with an intense psionic energy,

up.description: A surge of illithid activity seems to occur above you.

32535.title: Within the Strange Chamber
32535.description:
All around you, strange hunched figures regard you with a mixture of disdain
and contempt before continuing about their business.  The beings are dark and
covered in tattered rags, as the physical realm means little to them. The walls
of this place shimmer and hum with an intense psionic energy, acting more as
mental barriers than physical ones.  It is almost as if the architect of this
place used sheer imagination and mental will to construct the form of this
area.

west.description: A concentration of energy beckons you.

32538.title: Within a Strange Alcove
32538.description:
One would think that the concept of 'commerce' is beneath such creatures
as the illithid, but yet here lies what must only be construed as a shop.
There is nothing to distinguish this alcove from the others, yet the walls
of this place shimmer and hum with an intense psionic energy, acting more as
mental barriers than physical ones.  It is almost as if the architect of this
alcove used sheer imagination and mental will to construct its form.

32542.title: A Source of Psionic Energy
32542.description:
A humming portal beckons and repels you simulatenously here. Memories of
psychic, emotional, mental, and physiological overload flood your mind,
bringing back the horrors of the vertigo chambers  Yer something also
pulls you closer, gnawing at your curiosity.

32545.title: Humming Ethereal Passage
32545.description:
As with before, the crackling portal seals shut as you exit, leaving you in
a violently humming tunnel.  The walls of this place are made of a strange
ethereal fabric that is spongy and sticky to the touch, while a stream of vile
looking ooze courses along the floor. The walls hum with an intsense psionic
energy, and seem to register your unwelcome presence with hostility.  You feel
your mind exerting a constant effort justto keep a strange presence from
turning your brain to scrambled eggs. The effort to focus is exhausting, yet
the flow of mana coursing its way through your body also seems to be increased.
You may continue down the ethereal passage to the east.

32554.title: End of the Humming Ethereal Passage
32554.description:
You are at the base of a violently humming tunnel. A purple and black tear in
the fabric of reality floats in the center of the room, beckoning to you. The
walls of this place are made of a strange ethereal fabric that is spongy and
sticky to the touch, while a lake of vile looking ooze congeals beneath you.
The walls hum with an intsense psionic energy, and seem to register your
unwelcome presence with hostility. You feel your mind exerting a constant
effort justto keep a strange presence from turning your brain to scrambled
eggs. The effort to focus is exhausting, yet the flow of mana coursing its
way through your body also seems to be increased. You may ascend back up
the ethereal passage if you choose, but why bother?

32555.title: Floating in Nothingness
32555.description:
There is truly nothing your mind can detect in any shape or form as far as
the senses reveal in any direction.  The crackling portal that led you here
is gone, and the only thing providing you with any guidance whatsoever is
a strong surge of power coming from above.  A mass of congealed globulous
slimy water gathers beneath you.  How it got here and its purpose is not
easily ascertained.

extras.description:
You sense an impenetrable force preventing you from ascending.  You cannot
wrap your senses around it, but there must be a way to break through. If
not, you will likely spend the rest of your limited days wasting away in
this empty chamber of nothingness.

32556.title: Floating in Nothingness
32556.description:

the senses reveal in any direction.  The only thing providing you with any
guidance whatsoever is a strong surge of power coming from above.

extras.description:

32557.title: The Final Test
32557.description:
The surge of power coming from above is palpable here.  There is nothing else
worthy of your attention as you float your way up toward the source of this
unseen power.  Large glass tubes containing submerged slimy looking mauve
hivespawn react ominously at your presence, thumping and flopping uncomfortably
against their glass prisons.  A strange assortment of ethereal cords, synapses,
neurons and other brain-matter connect the tubes with a glowing source from
above. A humming and crackling psionic barricade prevents further ascension,
and you would be wise not to approach it without the necessary clearance.

extras.description:
The defenses of this barricade are indeed impenetrable. An incomprehensible
power infuses the barrier with psionic and spiritual energy so strong, that
attempting to touch it sends ripples of mind-rending shockwaves through your
brain, destroying synapses and neurons.  Something must allow passage, though,
lest you spend the rest of your limited days wasting away in this empty chamber
of nothingness.

32558.title: Hivemind Cortex
32558.description:
Alarms ring inside your mind that this is a very dangerous place! You are
surrounded from head to toe by all manner of wispy nerves and cords, which
serve to connect the mother brain to all her hive children and the ethereal
fabric of the hive itself. Her last defense breached, the mother brain will
destroy any invader with immense shockwaves of psionic energy.

extras.description:

32573.title: Mind Trap
32573.description:
You have mistakenly wandered into one of the hive's many mind traps, designed
to mislead and entrap unwelcome visitors to the hive lair.  There appears to
be no way out, though perhaps death will save you.  You have little time to
wallow in your confusion and despair, as the hive's "cleaning" robot appears
to have been dispatched to end your brief visit.

32582.title: Humming Ethereal Passage
32582.description:
You are in a violently humming tunnel. The walls of this place are made of a
strange ethereal fabric that is spongy and sticky to the touch, while a stream
of vile looking ooze courses along the floor. The walls hum with an intsense
psionic energy, and seem to register your unwelcome presence with hostility.
You feel your mind exerting a constant effort justto keep a strange presence
from  turning your brain to scrambled eggs. The effort to focus is exhausting,
yet the flow of mana coursing its way through your body also seems to be
increased. You may follow the passage west or descend here.

32588.title: Mind Trap
32588.description:
You have mistakenly wandered into one of the hive's many mind traps, designed
to mislead and entrap unwelcome visitors to the hive lair.  There appears to
be no way out, though perhaps death will save you.  You have little time to
wallow in your confusion and despair, as the hive's "cleaning" robot appears
to have been dispatched to end your brief visit.

32589.title: Ascending out of the Darkness
32589.description:
The crackling and shimmering portal remains open behind you, but your desire
to go back is plagued by painful memories of mental anguish. This earthy
tunnel is damp and smells like spring rains. A celestial light shines from
above, searing your eyes which have become so accustomed to darkness.

32590.title: Ascending out of the Darkness
32590.description:
This earthy tunnel is damp and smells like spring rains. A celestial light
shines from above, searing your eyes which have become so accustomed to
the darkness.

32591.title: A Strange Alcove
32591.description:
This earthy tunnel is damp and smells like spring rains. A celestial light
shines from above, searing your eyes which have become so accustomed to
the darkness.  You can make out some large antechambers hollowed out in the
walls here as if someone hastily was looking to conceal something.
The markings on the antechamber walls draw your attention.

extras.description:
Whoever carved out the earth here was no dwarf or gnome.  The work is shoddy
at best, and downright mediocre at its worst.  Gnarled roots and knots with
clumps of earth protrude from odd angles, and the ground is very uneven. A
small series of markings have been scored into the walls of the chamber, but
they seem barely legible.

Upon closer inspection these markings actually appear to be runes covered
etched into the surface of the chamber floor. The words are in a strange
language you cannot decipher, but you cannot help but wonder why someone
would go to all this trouble to leave mark the chamber with such bizarre
runes.

As it turns out, the runes in the antechamber have not been carved here at
all, but instead have been etched into the surface by an acidic slime that
cinged away the dirt.  There is still a bit of an acrid odor lingering in
this place, making you wonder just how long ago this slimy etching was
made.

The slime here has congealed into a large puddle just beneath the surface
of the runic etchings.  It looks like the ooze somehow crystallized after
serving its purpose to demarcate something or someone here.

32592.title: A clean and bare room
32592.description:
The earthy tunnel has come to an abrupt end at a white tiled room. There
is no sign of activity, or dirt from below.  The room itself actually feels
quit sterile.  Almost unspoiled to the point of making you feel slightly
uncomfortable lingering here. An incandescent light shines from an unknown
source, illuminating a final shimmering portal.  This one, however, appears
to be free of any dark energy, and peering through it reveals signs of life.

down.description: An earthy tunnel leads down to an antechamber.

32593.title: Invasion Chamber
32593.description:
This room serves as the primary nexus for the inhabitants of the hive to
invade the surface in conquest of yet more brains upon which to feed and
nourish the hivemind.  A shimmering and crackling psionic portal in the center
of the room is the focus of attention as illithid creatures occasionally enter
the chamber and flit through the portal.  The chamber walls shimmer and hum
with an intense psionic energy, acting more as mental barriers than physical
ones.  It is almost as if the architect of this Chamber used sheer imagination
and mental will to construct its form.

down.description: A strange intersection lies below you.
